WEBVTT

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:14.959
For old times' sake

00:01:14.959 --> 00:01:17.359
I'll let you hear Ruochu's voice one last time

00:01:17.359 --> 00:01:17.879
Alright

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:37.200
Hello

00:01:37.879 --> 00:01:38.319
Ruochu

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:39.120
Chen Fan

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:39.840
Ruochu

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:41.280
Chen Fan

00:01:41.519 --> 00:01:42.599
Chen Fan, where are you

00:01:42.719 --> 00:01:43.239
Chen Fan

00:01:43.519 --> 00:01:44.439
Ruochu

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:45.680
Ruochu

00:01:45.879 --> 00:01:48.719
Why do you always only remember Chen Fan

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:50.560
Chen Fan

00:01:51.719 --> 00:01:54.959
Ruochu, don't listen to him

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:56.159
Chen Fan

00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:57.280
You are always like this

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.480
Always ignoring me

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:08.520
Ruochu

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.560
I've figured it out now

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:12.479
I think that you now

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:14.039
In my heart

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:17.159
Are nothing more than a minor character

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:18.319
Zhou Honghai

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:19.280
Where is Chen Fan

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:20.240
Chen Fan

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:22.439
I used to think you were too important

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.479
There was absolutely no need

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:32.319
Chen Fan

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.199
Chen Fan

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.280
Chen Fan

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.840
Chen Fan, say something

00:02:44.879 --> 00:02:45.639
Chen Fan

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:50.639
Chen Fan

00:02:50.639 --> 00:02:52.400
Chen Fan, say something

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:55.680
Choose. Let time be rewritten

00:02:56.199 --> 00:02:58.599
Let her be free from her entanglement with you

00:02:58.919 --> 00:03:00.479
Saved by another man

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:01.919
Without you

00:03:02.199 --> 00:03:04.080
But safe and happy from now on

00:03:04.479 --> 00:03:06.759
Living a peaceful and smooth life

00:03:14.199 --> 00:03:15.120
I am willing

00:03:17.039 --> 00:03:18.840
If Ruochu can be happy

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:23.080
I am willing

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.039
You're awake

00:03:59.439 --> 00:03:59.960
Don't worry

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:00.960
The surgery was very successful

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.319
The internal bruising and fractures have been treated

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:07.560
Doctor

00:04:08.199 --> 00:04:09.039
Where is Su Ruochu

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:10.039
What

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:10.840
How is she

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.599
We don't have anyone by that name here

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:22.600
So she's really gone

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:28.759
Gone is good

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.079
Gone is good

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:35.720
Good

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:44.160
Long Technologies

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.399
Suspected of illegal smuggling, illegal monopoly

00:04:46.399 --> 00:04:47.920
Shielding criminals, and other charges

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:50.160
The police have formally opened an investigation

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:53.040
The investors behind it will be investigated according to the law

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:02.680
That's great

00:05:03.079 --> 00:05:04.199
Finally took down their nest

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:05.240
Serves them right

00:05:09.079 --> 00:05:09.680
Bro is awake

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:10.879
Bro, Chen Fan

00:05:10.879 --> 00:05:11.360
Bro

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.720
You're finally awake

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.639
You scared me to death

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:15.079
Chen Fan, look

00:05:15.319 --> 00:05:16.279
Long Technologies has fallen

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:17.000
Bro

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:18.279
Thank you for saving my sister

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.079
Bro

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:19.879
Are you okay

00:05:19.879 --> 00:05:22.759
Don't touch me, it hurts

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.319
Scared me to death

00:05:27.839 --> 00:05:28.639
Doctor

00:05:30.079 --> 00:05:31.399
Doctor, Chen Fan is awake

00:05:31.399 --> 00:05:31.879
Chen Fan is awake

00:05:31.879 --> 00:05:32.680
Don't rush, don't rush

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:33.839
I'll go find the doctor for you

00:05:34.079 --> 00:05:34.879
Please hurry

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.319
He just woke up.

00:05:49.439 --> 00:05:50.279
He needs to rest properly.

00:05:50.399 --> 00:05:51.199
Stop making a fuss, everyone.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:52.040
Cut it out.

00:05:58.519 --> 00:05:59.439
Bro.

00:05:59.439 --> 00:06:00.720
We missed you to death.

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.759
The doctor said...

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.680
...he can't move around.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:06.160
Do you miss us?

00:06:07.279 --> 00:06:07.959
Chen Fan.

00:06:16.199 --> 00:06:17.519
Sis, you're back.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.040
I just went to testify.

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:26.839
Do you know?

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:28.560
Lawyer Zhang has linked...

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:29.680
...all the evidence together.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:30.959
It's an ironclad case.

00:06:31.199 --> 00:06:33.439
Long Technologies and Zhou Honghai can't escape.

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:47.879
You still remember?

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:50.959
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:06:51.279 --> 00:06:52.439
Things from two lifetimes...

00:06:52.759 --> 00:06:53.560
...I remember them all.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.519
In my past life...

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:28.360
...I seemed to have everything as I lay in a hospital bed.

00:07:28.879 --> 00:07:30.560
With only the ticking of machines beside me.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:33.240
I couldn't even find someone to sign for me.

00:07:34.279 --> 00:07:35.199
I became President Chen...

00:07:35.839 --> 00:07:37.160
...but what good was a mountain of money?

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:39.319
Fortunately...

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:41.399
...everything is different now.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:43.480
Friends and my love...

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:44.920
...are all by my side.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:51.440
Unity is strength.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.559
Come on, bottoms up. I'm drinking it all.

00:08:52.559 --> 00:08:54.039
Bottoms up.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.120
I'm finishing mine.

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:09.120
Ruochu.

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:10.799
I lost you in my past life.

00:09:11.039 --> 00:09:12.759
That was God's greatest punishment for me.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:17.799
Being able to hold your hand tight in this life...

00:09:18.639 --> 00:09:20.480
...is the greatest fulfillment of my two lives.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:21.879
Ruochu.

00:09:21.879 --> 00:09:22.360
Chen Fan.

00:09:24.879 --> 00:09:25.759
Let's get married.

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:29.000
Get married!

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:40.360
There.

00:09:41.559 --> 00:09:42.360
Locked in tight.

00:09:44.759 --> 00:09:45.720
This life...

00:09:46.799 --> 00:09:49.159
...past life, and next life.

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:51.000
Let's be together happily.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:53.039
Don't ever run away from my side again.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.159
Okay?

00:09:56.559 --> 00:09:57.080
Bro.

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:58.360
You're really something.

00:09:58.639 --> 00:09:59.759
In a few years, you went from a small boss...

00:09:59.759 --> 00:10:00.960
...to a big boss in a flash.

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.480
And proposing to the campus belle.

00:10:02.759 --> 00:10:04.159
You're simply a winner in life.

00:10:04.399 --> 00:10:05.440
Invincible.

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:08.799
Totally invincible.

00:10:10.639 --> 00:10:11.519
Invincible.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:13.799
Yeah.

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:16.000
As long as you guys are here...

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:17.600
...and Ruochu is here...

00:10:18.600 --> 00:10:19.879
...I'll definitely be invincible.